1. *Dvanaest* godina imam. (I am twelve years old.)
2. Videli smo *dvanaest* ptica na grani. (We saw twelve birds on the branch.)
3. *Dvanaest* sati dnevno radim. (I work twelve hours a day.)
4. Našli smo *dvanaest* jabuka u bašti. (We found twelve apples in the garden.)
5. *Dvanaest* je meseci u godini. (There are twelve months in a year.)
6. Potrebno je *dvanaest* ljudi da pomeri ovaj kamen. (It takes twelve people to move this rock.)
7. Koliko je *dvanaest* plus pet? (*Twelve* plus five is?)
8. Kupio sam *dvanaest* knjiga u knjižari. (I bought twelve books at the bookstore.)
9. *Dvanaest* pitanja je bilo na ispitu. (There were twelve questions on the exam.)
10. *Dvanaest* riba pliva u akvarijumu. (There are twelve fish swimming in the aquarium.)